<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Blog Website</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-SnH5WK+bZxgPHs44uWIX+LLJAJ9/2PkPKZ5QiAj6Ta86w+fsb2TkcmfRyVX3pBnMFcV7oQPJkl9QevSCWr3W6A=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="site">
      <%- include("../views/partials/navabar.ejs") %>
      <main>
        <div class="container">
          <section class="main-content">
            <h2 class="center">Our Blog</h2>
            <h1 class="center">Stories & Ideas</h1>
            <p class="center">
              Explore breathtaking landscapes, iconic landmarks, and hidden gems
              around the globe
            </p>
            <div class="content-grid">
              <div class="blog-post">
                <img
                  src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x400"
                  alt="Mount Fuji"
                />
                <div class="post-content">
                  <span class="category">TRAVEL</span>
                  <h2>Unveiling The Majestic Beauty Of Mount Fuji</h2>
                  <p>
                    A Journey To Japan's Iconic Symbol And Natural Wonder.
                    Discover The Rich History, Breathtaking Landscapes, And
                    Cultural Significance Of This Iconic Landmark
                  </p>
                  <span class="tags"
                    ><a href="">Read</a><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i
                  ></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <aside class="sidebar">
                <h3>Top Stories</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <img
                      src="https://via.placeholder.com/60"
                      alt="Mountains and Boat"
                    />
                    <div class="story-info">
                      <h4>Mountains and Boat: A Perfect Harmony</h4>
                      <p>John Smith • 24 Jan 2023</p>
                      <span class="top-stoies-read"
                        ><a href="">Read</a><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i
                      ></span>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <img
                      src="https://via.placeholder.com/60"
                      alt="Old Street"
                    />
                    <div class="story-info">
                      <h4>
                        Unveiling the Timeless Charm of Old Street Buildings
                      </h4>
                      <p>John Smith • 24 Jan 2023</p>
                      <span class="top-stoies-read"
                        ><a href="">Read</a><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i
                      ></span>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <img
                      src="https://via.placeholder.com/60"
                      alt="Whispering Trees"
                    />
                    <div class="story-info">
                      <h4>Whispering Trees and the Enchanting Moon</h4>
                      <p>John Smith • 24 Jan 2023</p>
                      <span class="top-stoies-read"
                        ><a href="">Read</a><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i
                      ></span>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </aside>
            </div>
            <div class="additional-posts">
              <div class="post">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200" alt="City" />
                <div class="post-content">
                  <span class="author">Candice Wu • 15 Jan 2022</span>
                  <h3>The Pulse of the City Unfolds on the Fast Lanes</h3>
                  <p>
                    Embark on an exhilarating ride through the bustling urban
                    highways, where the rhythm of the city echoes in the hum of
                    engines and the dazzling lights of the skyline.
                  </p>
                  <span class="tags"
                    ><a href="">Read</a><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i
                  ></span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="post">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200" alt="Cosmos" />
                <div class="post-content">
                  <span class="author">Alec Whitman • 17 Jan 2022</span>
                  <h3>A Cosmic Adventure Underneath the Starlit Canopy</h3>
                  <p>
                    Embark on an extraordinary odyssey as we merge the realms of
                    mankind, automotive marvels, and the awe-inspiring Milky
                    Way. Join us on a celestial journey through the cosmos.
                  </p>
                  <span class="tags"
                    ><a href="">Read</a><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i
                  ></span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </main>
      <%- include("../views/partials/footer.ejs") %>
    </div>
    <script src="/javascripts/home.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
